divs: Sighting DetailsI was outside in the cornfield just playing around with the camera. I did not even see the object until I downloaded the pictures onto my computer. The bottom looks like it is glowing white with a little green and the top looks blue. It only showed up in this one picture. I thought this is cool, I got something pretty neat here. I emailed the picture to a few friends to get opinions. Everyone says it looks like a UFO.
Summary: Did not see this object when taking pictures
